servicecatalog:ResourceType.description: Filters access by controlling what value can be specified as the ResourceType parameter in an AppRegistry associate resource API

servicecatalog:accountLevel.description: Filters access by user to see and perform actions on resources created by anyone in the account

servicecatalog:userLevel.description: Filters access by user to see and perform actions on only resources that they created
